---
title: Sri Lankan Shrimp Pilaf with Beet and Herb Slaw
description: Sri Lanka - they call it the pearl of India - because it really is that beautiful. Seafood is one of its main treasures and we’ve added gorgeous beets, because they're in season and they add a beautiful hue to the dish!
